### ============================================
### JRC SportSync API Testing
### ============================================
### Use REST Client extension in VS Code
### Install: humao.rest-client

POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your_token_here

{ 
    "message": "book a basketball court for tomorrow at 3 PM for 1 hour no adds on",
    "userId": "93871edc-5eae-2657-bdd0-5b05b6910338" 
}


### HEALTH CHECK
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### ROOT/INFO
GET http://localhost:3000/

### ============================================
### BOOKINGS ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get user bookings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/u1

### Check court availability
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/court1/availability?date=2026-05-15&startTime=14:00&endTime=15:00

### Create a booking
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "u1",
  "court_id": "court1",
  "booking_date": "2026-05-15",
  "start_time": "14:00",
  "end_time": "15:00",
  "addons": []
}

### Cancel booking
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/b1

### ============================================
### COACHES ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### List all coaches
GET http://localhost:3000/api/coaches

### Request coaching session
POST http://localhost:3000/api/coaches/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coach_id": "c1",
  "user_id": "u1",
  "sport_id": "basketball",
  "session_date": "2026-05-20",
  "start_time": "16:00",
  "end_time": "17:00"
}

### ============================================
### PAYMENTS ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Process payment
POST http://localhost:3000/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": "b1",
  "amount": 450,
  "payment_method": "gcash"
}

### Get payment details
GET http://localhost:3000/api/payments/pay_123456

### ============================================
### USERS ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get user profile
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/u1

### Update user profile
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/u1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "phone": "+63 9XX XXX XXXX"
}

### Get loyalty points
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/u1/loyalty

### Get user booking history
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/u1/bookings

### ============================================
### ADMIN ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get analytics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/analytics

### Get pending requests (cancellations & coaching verifications)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/pending-requests

### Verify coaching payment
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/verify-payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "cp1"
}

### Approve cancellation request
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/approve-cancellation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "cr1"
}